«ac»«c6»Amiga Demo:«»
«»
«as»«c7»Competition Machine is an A1200, 68060, 50Mhz with 2 MB chip and 32 MB fastram.
Maximum running time is 10 min, and must be exitable with left mouse button, 
at any time
during the presentation.
The demo must be HD installable and preferably with a HD-Installer, and should 
not be
larger than 8MB installed.
Only one demo per coder.«»
«»
Note: The demo have to run on an A1200 68030 with fpu with 2 MB chip and 8 MB 
fast.«»
