«ac»«c6»PC Demo Accelerated:«»
«»
«as»«c7»Competition Machine is an AMD 1.2GHz, 256MB RAM, Soundblaster Live and a
Nvidia GeForce 2 Graphics card.
Demo size Max 8MB installed and a maximum of 10 min running time.
The demo will be run under Windows. Must support OpenGL or Direct 3D and run 
on other
OpenGL/D3D cards.
It must be exitable with escape anytime during the presentation.
Only one demo per coder.«»
